claim.claim-text:
1. A data regeneration device comprising: 
a plurality of despreading units for regenerating pilot and data signals by means of pilot and data Walsh codes; 
a path controller for selectively activating the despreading units; 
an antenna-waiting signal generator for creating an antenna-waiting signal using the pilot signals output from the despreading units; 
an adder for summing the data signals output from the despreading units; and 
a controller to control the path controller and the adder in accordance with a transmission scheme of a base station.
